---
import Carousel from "../components/Carousel.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Radiodent Radiologia Odontológica - Panorâmica - Tomografia - Radiografia - Madureira RJ"
>
  <main class="container-fluid px-0">
    <div
      class="px-4 py-5 text-center hero-image d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center"
    >
      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold main-color">Bem vindo a Radiodent</h1>
      <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
        <p class="lead mb-4">
          Há 24 anos, a Radiodent tem sido um ponto de referência em Madureira,
          oferecendo serviços odontológicos de alta qualidade e excelência.
          Nossa equipe altamente qualificada está comprometida em proporcionar o
          melhor atendimento aos nossos pacientes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 whatsapp-bg py-5 px-5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <h2>Quem somos</h2>
              <p></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <Carousel />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5" id="featured-3">
      <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">Columns with icons</h2>
      <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
        <div class="feature col">
          <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-gradient">
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"
              ><use xlink:href="#collection"></use></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h2>Featured title</h2>
          <p>
            Paragraph of text beneath the heading to explain the heading. We'll
            add onto it with another sentence and probably just keep going until
            we run out of words.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="icon-link">
            Call to action
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"
              ><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg
            >
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="feature col">
          <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-gradient">
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"
              ><use xlink:href="#people-circle"></use></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h2>Featured title</h2>
          <p>
            Paragraph of text beneath the heading to explain the heading. We'll
            add onto it with another sentence and probably just keep going until
            we run out of words.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="icon-link">
            Call to action
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"
              ><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg
            >
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="feature col">
          <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-gradient">
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"
              ><use xlink:href="#toggles2"></use></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h2>Featured title</h2>
          <p>
            Paragraph of text beneath the heading to explain the heading. We'll
            add onto it with another sentence and probably just keep going until
            we run out of words.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="icon-link">
            Call to action
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"
              ><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg
            >
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .custom-home-circle-icon {
    background-color: rgba(6, 6, 6, 0.2) !important ;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
  }

  .hero-image {
    background-image: url("/images/hero-image.png");
    background-size: cover;
    min-height: 70vh;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  .whatsapp-bg {
    background-color: #1db954;
  }

  .custom-border-slide {
    border-bottom: 16px solid #1db954;
  }

  .pool-carousel-inner {
    overflow-x: hidden;
    overflow-y: auto;
    touch-action: pan-y pinch-zoom;
  }
</style>
